name: ENS: Ethereum Name Service
description: Ethereum Name Service (ENS) domains are secure domain names for the decentralized world. ENS domains provide a way for users to map human readable names to blockchain and non-blockchain resources, like Ethereum addresses, IPFS hashes, or website URLs. ENS domains can be bought and sold on secondary markets.

name: LonelyPop
description: LonelyPop is an art centered and community focused collectible NFT project residing on the Ethereum blockchain as a collection of unique, non-fungible tokens (NFTs) contrived of a combination of traits associated with underlying personalities & characteristics. LonelyPop was created with the intention of emphasizing the importance of mental health and specifically the challenges of loneliness.

name: Isekai Meta
description: Isekai Meta is a story and community-driven, hand-drawn NFT collection + metaverse brand that taps into the foundational human need to connect with others through story.
